      wl_kicker:'Demo version · fictional data', wl_claim:'The management system that walks every nurse from the Dominican Republic to the Italian ward',
      wl_start:'Start the guided tour', wl_explore:'Explore freely',
      wl_s1_title:'Analytics Dashboard', wl_s1_text:'Real-time KPIs, transfer summary, risk lights on cases stuck beyond their SLA and expiring documents: the whole project at a glance.',
      wl_s2_title:'Guided path: 9 phases, 2 teams', wl_s2_text:'Every candidate is a case moving through sequential phases — from the Dominican Republic Team (selection, documents, training, travel) to the Italy Team (arrival, housing, matching, employment, support) — with mandatory checklists, automatic gates and a full activity log. In the demo, Ana shows a case blocked by missing documents and out of SLA.',
      wl_s3_title:'Built-in GDPR privacy', wl_s3_text:'Bilingual Italian/Spanish consent form, prefilled and printable; upload the signed scan and the consent records itself in the candidate’s file.',
      wl_s4_title:'Document lifecycle', wl_s4_text:'Upload, review and approval, optional documents, monitored expiry dates and an archive with preview — all manageable straight from the personal record.',
      wl_s5_title:'From arrival to tailored matching', wl_s5_text:'Welcome, housing, matching hospital requests with candidates’ skills, contract and tutor: the Italy Team follows the nurse to full integration — in the demo, Rosa’s and Elena’s journeys.',
      wl_s6_title:'And much more', wl_s6_text:'In-app regulatory guide and operator manual, three languages, dark theme, admin/operator roles and one-click demo reset.',
      wl_s7_title:'Real-time alerts', wl_s7_text:'When a facility files a request or a request is fully staffed, an alert flags it to the whole team at once — even when the action comes from another operator.',
      wl_s8_title:'Candidate sheet as PDF', wl_s8_text:'From any case you generate a complete sheet — profile, contacts, skills, documents and log — ready to print or save as PDF for consulates and facilities.',
      wl_scroll:'Scroll to explore', wl_more:'Learn more', wl_back:'Close',
      wl_cta_title:'Ready to see DHL Nurses at work?', wl_cta_sub:'Start the step-by-step guided tour, or explore the demo data freely.',
      ld_s1:'<b>The whole project on one screen.</b><ul><li>Live KPIs: in management, transferred, to transfer, in matching, expiring documents, completed journeys.</li><li>Risk lights on cases stuck past the phase SLA.</li><li>Passport and cédula expiry watched and shown here, not only in the sheet.</li><li>Breakdown by facility and CSV export.</li></ul>',
      ld_s2:'<b>Nine phases, two teams.</b><ul><li>Dominican Republic team (phases 1–4): selection, documents, training, travel.</li><li>Italy team (phases 5–9): arrival, housing, matching, work, tutor.</li><li>Mandatory per-phase checklists and a document gate: no advancing until everything is ready.</li><li>Each operator works only their team’s phases; full log of who did what.</li></ul>',
      ld_s3:'<b>Compliant consent, no lost paper.</b><ul><li>Bilingual IT/ES GDPR form, pre-filled with the candidate’s data.</li><li>Printable and signable; uploading the scan records consent automatically with a date.</li><li>Consent revocation is tracked in the log.</li></ul>',
      ld_s4:'<b>From upload to approval.</b><ul><li>Upload (PDF or photo), review, approve or reject; status always colour-coded.</li><li>Optional documents that don’t block the pipeline; expiries monitored.</li><li>Archive with preview and search; upload straight from the profile too.</li></ul>',
      ld_s5:'<b>The right person in the right place.</b><ul><li>Facilities file requests with ward, shifts and minimum/preferred skills.</li><li>The shortlist is ranked by fit: eligible, score, documents and validated dossier.</li><li>Multiple matches per request; the seat frees up if the candidate is removed.</li></ul>',
      ld_s6:'<b>And the essentials around it.</b><ul><li>In-app regulatory guide and operator manual, in three languages.</li><li>Light/dark theme, admin/operator roles.</li><li>Full data backup to a file and one-click restore.</li></ul>',
      ld_s7:'<b>No request slips through.</b><ul><li>Instant alert when a facility files a new request.</li><li>Alert when a request becomes fully staffed.</li><li>In the real app, alerts also arrive from other operators’ actions, in real time.</li></ul>',
      ld_s8:'<b>A ready dossier in one click.</b><ul><li>Complete sheet: profile, contacts, skills, status/phase.</li><li>Document table with status and validity, plus the latest log entries.</li><li>Direct print or save as PDF from the browser.</li></ul>',
